jibe.sdk.client
Class JibeServiceResult

java.lang.Object
  jibe.sdk.client.JibeServiceResult
Direct Known Subclasses:
CallServiceResult, ChatSessionServiceResult, ContactsServiceResult, FileTransferServiceResult, MyProfileServiceResult, VideoSharingResult
public class JibeServiceResult
extends java.lang.Object

The Result object that gets returned from all calls to Jibe Realtime Engines. Used by client applications, in order to check whether the requested operation succeeeded, and to obtain the cause of failure if the requested operation could not be completed.

Field Summary

static int ERROR_SESSION_NOT_FOUND
